Cheesecake
This is a cheesecake like no other, with a soft cream mix that’s perfectly formed to create a sinfully
delicate texture, it’s the best made-from-scratch cheesecake you will ever have!
Golden, flaky spiral pastries wrapped around a mixture of melty
cheeses, Mozzarella, Ricotta, and Parmesan blended with spinach,
then glazed with honey and finished with crispy rosemary and a

This is the ideal comforting bowl of soup for a chilly winter Sunday
it’s filled with hearty vegetables and savory lentils cooked down in a
deliciously rich broth to warm you from the inside out.
Primavera Rosé Pasta
The perfect vegetarian pasta. Beginning with our robust and tangy rosé sauce which is created by
cooking down tomatoes, onions, garlic, and a touch of cream then adding a mixture of sauteed
garden vegetables and tossing it with our freshly made in house fettuccine pasta
Braciole- Italian Steak Roulade Brasied in Marinara
Tenderized thin slices of steak seasoned with fresh herbs, and garlic then rolled into a roulade and
stuffed with more herbs, garlic, grated cheeses and breadcrumb. Finally it’s braised in a pan of
simmering rich marinara sauce until fork tender and cut into spirals. Pronounced braa·chee·ow·lay
this is a favorite classic Italian dish served for Sunday family gatherings.
